query:
UPDATE learning_strategies SET
                strategy_type = $3,
                daily_target_items = $4,
                new_items_per_day = $5,
                difficulty_threshold = $6,
                learning_speed_factor = $7,
                retention_priority = $8,
                adaptive_scheduling = $9,
                last_adjusted_at = $10,
                version = version + 1,
                updated_at = NOW()
            WHERE user_id = $1 AND id = $2 AND version = $11
